NK041(di)050:0: rdzogs pa chen po gzhi lam 'bras bu dbyer med
NK041(di)050:1: pa'i don la smon pa rig stong rdo rje'i rang
NK041(di)050:2: gdangs zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK041(di)050:3: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bde gshegs sras bcas kyi //
NK041(di)050:4: ye shes skur gyur gnyis med tshul 'chang ba //
NK041(di)050:5: 'jam dpal gzhon nu mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang //
NK041(di)050:6: byar med don la lhun gyis grub gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:7: gdod ma'i mgon po dpal ldan bla ma la //
NK041(di)050:8: mnyam nyid chos skur lta ba'i mos gus kyis //
NK041(di)050:9: don rgyud dgongs pa'i byin rlabs snying la 'phos //
NK041(di)050:10: rig pa rtsal gyi dbang chen thob par shog /
NK041(di)050:11: ye nas gnas phyir rtsol bas sgrub pa dang //
NK041(di)050:12: dbang po'i khyad par sogs la mi ltos kyang //
NK041(di)050:13: sla bas yid ma ches pa sems kyi gsang //
NK041(di)050:14: bla ma'i man ngag stobs kyis mthong gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:15: spros shing dpyad pa kun rtog bsnon ma ste //
NK041(di)050:16: btsal zhing sgrub pa rang nyid ngal ba'i rgyu //
NK041(di)050:17: dmigs shing sgom pa phyir zhing 'ching ba'i gzeb //
NK041(di)050:18: zug rngu'i spros pa nang nas chod par shog /
NK041(di)050:19: bsam brjod bral la mthong ba gang med kyang //
NK041(di)050:20: ma mthong lhag mar gyur pa gang yang med //
NK041(di)050:21: rang sems kho thag chod pa zab mo'i don //
NK041(di)050:22: mtshon par dka' ba'i de nyid rtogs par shog /
NK041(di)050:23: spros kun ka nas dag phyir yod mtha' spangs //
NK041(di)050:24: rig gdangs lhun gyis grub pas med mtha' bral //
NK041(di)050:25: gnyis su brjod kyang rtog pas 'jug tshul tsam //
NK041(di)050:26: dbyer med brjod bral mnyam pa'i don mthong shog /
NK041(di)050:27: 'di na 'dzub mos zla ba ji bzhin du //
NK041(di)050:28: dang por yid dpyod tshig gis mtshon byas kyang //
NK041(di)050:29: chos nyid rang bab yid dpyod yul las 'das //
NK041(di)050:30: rang gis rang la blan te mthong bar shog /
NK041(di)050:31: 'di la bsal bar bya ba ma mthong zhing //
NK041(di)050:32: bzhag ste bsgrub par bya ba ma dmigs pas //
NK041(di)050:33: dgag sgrub rtsol bas ma bslad chos nyid ngang //
NK041(di)050:34: lhun gyis sgrub pa'i don la 'jug par shog /
NK041(di)050:35: shes bya'i gzhi dang bgrod par byed pa'i lam //
NK041(di)050:36: thob bya 'bras bu'i chos su btags pa yang //
NK041(di)050:37: rang bzhin gshis la nam mkha'i go rim 'dra //
NK041(di)050:38: byar med don la lhun gyis gnas par shog /
NK041(di)050:39: 'khrul pas sgro btags ma dag 'khor ba'i chos //
NK041(di)050:40: de las log pa dag pa'i snang ba yang //
NK041(di)050:41: ltos nas btags pa rnam par spros pa'i chos //
NK041(di)050:42: spros med gshis la mi gnas mthong gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:43: blo bral chos nyid gshis kyi bzhugs tshul la //
NK041(di)050:44: lta dang sgom pa'i bslad kyin rtog pas bsgribs //
NK041(di)050:45: tha mal gshis su son la lta sgom bral //
NK041(di)050:46: rnal ma'i don la bab kyis gnas gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:47: gang la dmigs par byas pa lta ba'i dug /
NK041(di)050:48: gang zhig rtsol bas zin pa sgom pa'i skyon //
NK041(di)050:49: gang la blang dor bya ba spyod pa'i 'phrang //
NK041(di)050:50: zug rngu kun bral chos nyid mthong bar shog /
NK041(di)050:51: spros pa'i gzeb tu ma tshud rig pa'i gdangs //
NK041(di)050:52: blo bral mngon sum mthong la yid dpyod kyi //
NK041(di)050:53: zhags pas mkha' la mdud pa mi 'dor bar //
NK041(di)050:54: rang bzhag rnal ma'i don la mkhas gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:55: de tshe rang rig gzhon nu bum pa sku'i //
NK041(di)050:56: mkhyen cha rang 'od gsal ba 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK041(di)050:57: shes rab rang byung sgron ma'i snang ba yis //
NK041(di)050:58: sgrib pa'i mun pa 'thib po 'joms gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:59: ma bcos 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid la //
NK041(di)050:60: bcos ma'i lam gyis gsar du sgrub med pas //
NK041(di)050:61: rgyu las ma byung mthar thug 'bras bu'i don //
NK041(di)050:62: rang la ye nas gnas pa mthong bar shog /
NK041(di)050:63: yid dpyod tshig gi spun pa 'khrul pa'i lam //
NK041(di)050:64: ji ltar byas kyang rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba ste //
NK041(di)050:65: lung las ma byung rang gis rig bya ba'i //
NK041(di)050:66: man ngag zab mo snying la bsgom par shog /
NK041(di)050:67: gzung 'dzin sems ni ngo bo nyid kyis 'khrul //
NK041(di)050:68: gang ltar dmigs pa de bzhin nyid du min //
NK041(di)050:69: sems las ma byung rang byung ye shes sku //
NK041(di)050:70: nges pa don gyi sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK041(di)050:71: rig stong rig pa'i dbyings su chos thams cad //
NK041(di)050:72: mnyam pa nyid gyur thig le nyag gcig la //
NK041(di)050:73: 'khor 'das re dog zhig pa'i ngang tshul du //
NK041(di)050:74: mi gnas chos sku'i gtan srid zin par shog /
NK041(di)050:75: 'di ltar lus dang yul du snang ba yang //
NK041(di)050:76: rab rib bzhin du rtog pa'i dbang gis snang //
NK041(di)050:77: mi rtog ye shes chen po'i rang gdangs kyis //
NK041(di)050:78: chos zad gdod ma'i dbyings su sbyangs gyur cig /
NK041(di)050:79: de tshe mkha' dang mnyam pa'i ye shes sku //
NK041(di)050:80: phyogs dus mu mtha' srid du 'gro kun gyi //
NK041(di)050:81: phan bde'i don kun 'jo ba'i yid bzhin nor //
NK041(di)050:82: sgrib bral 'bras bu'i mthar thug thob par shog /
NK041(di)050:83: ces pa 'di ni dz+ny+aa na d+aa ki ni w+aa
NK041(di)050:84: ra hi'i rnam par 'phrul par yongs su grags pa
NK041(di)050:85: rje btsun bde skyong ye shes dbang mos rab tshes
NK041(di)050:86: me khyi zla tshes kyi dus dge bar bkra shis
NK041(di)050:88: shel dkar phreng ba rin po che'i rgyan ldan bcas
NK041(di)050:89: bka' yis bskul ba'i rkyen byas nas tshes de nyid
NK041(di)050:90: la mi pham 'jam dpal dgyes pa'am 'od gsal rdo
NK041(di)050:91: rje zhes bya ba'i rdzogs par bris pa ste /
NK041(di)050:92: rdzogs pa chen po'i grub mtha'i rang skad thun min
NK041(di)050:93: rang rkang tshugs par gang shar smras pa'i dge bas
NK041(di)050:94: 'gro kun gdod ma'i mgon po 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i
